join(uint8,uint64,uint64,uint16,address,.details: based on {_planterType} a planter can join as individual planter or member of an organization

params._organization: address of organization to be member of NOTE if join as a member of an organization, when that organization accept planter, planter status set to active
params._planterType: 1 for individual and 3 for member of organization

joinOrganization(address,uint64,uint64,u.details: admin add a plater as organization (planterType 2) so planterType 3 can be member of these planters.

params._assignedPlanterAddress: address of planter that tree assigned to
params._planter: address of planter who want to plant tree

returns._0: if a planter can plant a tree or not

params._planter: address of planter NOTE treeFactory contract can call this function NOTE change status to full supplyCap if plantedCount be equal with planter supplyCap after increase plantedCount by 1

returns._0: true in case of planter status is active {1}

reducePlantedCount(address).details: when tree plant of {_planter} rejected, plantedCount of {_planter} must reduce 1 time and if planter status is full supplyCap {2} update it to active {1}

params._planter: address of planter NOTE only treeFactory contract can call this function
